= Version History

== 1.0.5 / 2011-03-09:

* Removed an extraneous space from the #pretty_print output that has always
  bugged me. *So* worth a new release
* Added information and a usage example to the README

== 1.0.4 / 2011-01-09:

* Added a validation class method to the Parser class to help with error
  checking in applications

== 1.0.3 / 2011-01-08:

* Trying to fix version detection when building gem

== 1.0.2 / 2010-12-29:

* Fixed some busted require statements
* Expression#pretty_print writes to a string buffer instead of stdout

== 1.0.1 / 2010-12-26:

* Very minor changes to build and deploy configuration

== 1.0.0 / 2010-12-26:

* Wrote (more or less) complete documentation comments for all classes and
  methods
* Wrote a full suite of test cases that performs unit tests, functional tests,
  and integration tests
* Included a copy of the GNU GPLv3 in the root directory, and put GPL rights
  notices at the top of every file
* Packaged project up as a gem
